About this item    🌎GROUNDING: Grounding uses the earth's natural energy to improve health and well-being. The earth carries a slightly negative electrical charge. When you come into direct contact with the earth, either by standing barefoot or by using a grounding product, this charge is transferred to your body. In your body, these negatively charged free electrons work as antioxidants which neutralize the harmful free radicals and helps you to realize many health benefits.    👣HOW IT WORKS: Snap one end of the grounding cord onto the continuity tester and plug the other end into a grounded outlet. Then, place the continuity tester onto your grounding product and press the button. If the light remains green as you move the tester over the surface of the grounding product then that means it is successfully grounded and there is continuity. Please make sure the grounding product being tested is also plugged into a grounded outlet, or you will not have continuity.    👣WHATS INCLUDED: Our grounding continuity tester includes one tester with battery included, as well as a 15 foot grounding cord which will allow you to properly test for continuity, and can serve as a back up or replacement grounding cord for your grounding/earth connected products.    🔋BATTERY INCLUDED: One battery is included inside of the continuity tester. The tester is ready to be used once connected to a grounding cord!    👣INSTRUCTIONAL VIDEO: Please refer to the video in the product pictures for a guide on how to use this continuity tester.

A hum and then a click a few seconds later from the compressor indicates a compressor or relay issue but not a motherboard problem.
